OL,3,CMan jailed for nine years after
OL,4,Crobbing car with knife while on test
OL,5,Cdrive
OL,7,FA man from Birmingham who stole a car
OL,8,Fat knifepoint has been jailed for nine
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FLeroy Simpson admitted to robbery and
OL,12,Faggravated vehicle taking following an
OL,13,Fincident in February this year.
OL,15,FHe used a false name on social media
OL,16,Fand arranged to view a car in Great
OL,17,FBridgeford in Stafford that was being
OL,18,Fsold on Facebook marketplace.
