OL,3,CMan jailed for nine years after
OL,4,Crobbing car with knife while on test
OL,5,Cdrive
OL,7,FThe owner was sat in the passenger
OL,8,Fseat when Simpson took the car for a
OL,9,Ftest drive. He drove into a cul-de-sac
OL,10,Fand pulled a knife on the victim who
OL,11,Fgot out and ran away.
OL,13,FStaffordshire Police tracked the car
OL,14,Fdown while also tracing him in the air
OL,15,Fon a helicopter.
OL,17,FHe was followed until he jumped out of
OL,18,Fthe car and tried to flee on foot at
OL,19,FHopwood Services in Birmingham.
