OL,4,Crobbing car with knife while on test
OL,5,Cdrive
OL,7,FSimpson was found near a woodland and
OL,8,Farrested.
OL,10,FSimpson was sentenced to nine years at
OL,11,FStafford Crown Court on Monday 5th
OL,12,FAugust.
OL,14,FHe was also disqualified from driving
OL,15,Ffor eight years and five months, and
OL,16,Fordered to take an extended re-test.
OL,18,F"He could have easily caused serious
OL,19,Finjury or death"
