OL,4,Crobbing car with knife while on test
OL,5,Cdrive
OL,7,FPC Kadir Guler, the officer in charge
OL,8,Fof the case, said:
OL,10,F"We welcome the sentence given to
OL,11,FSimpson and hope it serves as clear
OL,12,Fmessage that such aggravated and
OL,13,Fserious crime in Stafford will not be
OL,14,Ftolerated.
OL,16,F"Simpson was callous in his efforts to
OL,17,Fmaintain his alter ego whilst
OL,18,Fcontinuing with his ulterior motive to
OL,19,Frob the car, proven by him taking a
OL,20,Fknife with him to the meeting.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
