OL,7,F"He could have easily caused serious
OL,8,Finjury or death whilst on his ten-mile
OL,9,Fdrive across the M5 which ended by him
OL,10,Fcrashing the stolen vehicle.
OL,12,F"The pursuit carried out was safe and
OL,13,Feffective and the skills held by NPAS
OL,14,Fmeant this offender was swiftly
OL,15,Fbrought to justice."
